WEBVTT

00:00:14.725 --> 00:00:18.487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

00:00:18.562 --> 00:00:22.162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:25.437
♪Your "same here" carries
a touch of resolve♪

00:00:25.862 --> 00:00:29.412
♪Pack my bags, we can set off right now♪

00:00:29.637 --> 00:00:33.112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:36.712
♪The journey itself is what
truly matters before the destination♪

00:00:36.787 --> 00:00:40.975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

00:00:41.025 --> 00:00:42.612
♪Connect♪

00:00:42.625 --> 00:00:43.275
♪Let's go!♪

00:00:43.612 --> 00:00:47.137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

00:00:47.237 --> 00:00:50.675
♪Today, no dwelling
on negative emotions♪

00:00:50.750 --> 00:00:53.450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:55.262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

00:00:55.262 --> 00:00:58.199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

00:00:59.075 --> 00:01:02.375
=Love In A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

00:01:02.675 --> 00:01:06.275
=Episode 3=

00:01:18.160 --> 00:01:19.320
Hua!

00:01:19.512 --> 00:01:21.072
Zhu.

00:01:21.072 --> 00:01:22.275
You're finally here.

00:01:22.275 --> 00:01:23.957
Why did you call me here in a hurry?

00:01:26.375 --> 00:01:27.855
We lack racers today.

00:01:27.855 --> 00:01:29.520
All outside bets are now closed,

00:01:29.775 --> 00:01:31.040
but we have no racers.

00:01:32.262 --> 00:01:33.200
Hua.

00:01:34.575 --> 00:01:35.735
Is this the competitor

00:01:35.735 --> 00:01:36.975
you brought today?

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:39.440
Can she even turn the steering wheel?

00:01:40.025 --> 00:01:41.425
I don't compete with girls.

00:01:42.100 --> 00:01:42.920
Hold it right there.

00:01:43.350 --> 00:01:44.590
It's not me.

00:01:46.512 --> 00:01:47.552
It's this guy.

00:01:48.500 --> 00:01:51.423
He's won the Formula 1 Championship
in the US, you know?

00:01:51.675 --> 00:01:53.435
What championship?

00:01:53.440 --> 00:01:54.472
I don't know how to drive.

00:01:54.472 --> 00:01:55.962
I was carsick just now, you know?

00:01:56.960 --> 00:01:58.840
Here, we have a rule.

00:01:58.840 --> 00:02:01.200
If the scheduled
competition is canceled,

00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:02.900
one has to pay two million yuan as a fine.

00:02:03.212 --> 00:02:04.732
Will you compete?

00:02:04.825 --> 00:02:06.412
Or will you pay the fine?

00:02:07.480 --> 00:02:09.880
Two million yuan.
Kid, will you take on the challenge?

00:02:10.137 --> 00:02:11.017
Kid,

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:14.280
racing can be deadly, you know?

00:02:15.760 --> 00:02:16.760
I'll pay the fine.

00:02:17.560 --> 00:02:19.400
There's another rule here.

00:02:19.800 --> 00:02:21.990
If the competitor arrives at the scene
and cancels the match,

00:02:22.360 --> 00:02:24.160
they have to pay a fine
of five million yuan.

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:26.560
Woohoo. Kid, we're talking
about five million yuan here.

00:02:31.560 --> 00:02:32.600
Have you made up your mind?

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:36.880
Bring it on, then.

00:03:08.880 --> 00:03:10.360
You brought me here

00:03:10.360 --> 00:03:11.960
so that I could embarrass myself, right?

00:03:16.090 --> 00:03:17.560
Let me show you what I'm capable of.

00:03:47.200 --> 00:03:50.200
Ready!

00:03:54.960 --> 00:03:56.280
Go!

00:05:44.600 --> 00:05:45.950
Have you lost your mind from that?

00:05:50.240 --> 00:05:51.850
What championship?

00:05:51.850 --> 00:05:52.898
I don't know how to drive.

00:05:52.898 --> 00:05:54.538
I was carsick just now, you know?

00:05:54.837 --> 00:05:56.477
So, were you pretending

00:05:57.487 --> 00:05:59.207
all along?

00:05:59.250 --> 00:06:01.625
You said I was a hypocrite, right?

00:06:02.200 --> 00:06:03.200
What do you think?

00:06:03.880 --> 00:06:05.000
Aren't I amazing?

00:06:20.300 --> 00:06:21.200
Get out of the way!

00:06:22.280 --> 00:06:23.960
How dare you trick me?

00:06:23.960 --> 00:06:24.640
Huh?

00:06:24.760 --> 00:06:26.000
What are you talking about?

00:06:26.440 --> 00:06:28.200
Who said we tricked you?

00:06:28.200 --> 00:06:30.040
You were just bad at driving.

00:06:30.040 --> 00:06:31.200
You two

00:06:31.200 --> 00:06:32.840
set me up and made me lose 200,000 yuan!

00:06:34.360 --> 00:06:36.120
Who told you to bet on our loss?

00:06:37.520 --> 00:06:38.720
You deserved this.

00:06:39.760 --> 00:06:40.600
What's wrong?

00:06:40.700 --> 00:06:42.260
Are you trying to be a sore loser now?

00:06:42.840 --> 00:06:44.760
You'd better take out the money now.

00:06:44.760 --> 00:06:46.840
If not, no one gets to leave!

00:06:50.480 --> 00:06:51.400
Beat him up!

00:06:52.320 --> 00:06:53.120
Beat him up!

00:06:54.120 --> 00:06:55.400
Beat him to death!

00:06:55.960 --> 00:06:56.880
Stop it!

00:06:59.600 --> 00:07:00.400
Stop!

00:07:03.600 --> 00:07:04.200
Jia,

00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:06.880
do not cause trouble in my territory.

00:07:29.560 --> 00:07:30.600
Be gentle.

00:07:31.960 --> 00:07:33.320
Can't you be gentle for once?

00:07:34.280 --> 00:07:35.560
Now, you know it hurts, huh?

00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:38.400
Weren't you pretty fierce just now?

00:07:44.950 --> 00:07:46.190
What is this?

00:07:46.800 --> 00:07:48.780
It's too childish.
Don't stick it on my face.

00:07:54.520 --> 00:07:55.880
I like it.

00:08:03.760 --> 00:08:05.120
I suppose

00:08:06.680 --> 00:08:08.040
you don't hate me that much.

00:08:09.120 --> 00:08:10.680
You aren't that detestable, I suppose.

00:08:23.480 --> 00:08:25.040
Why are you staring at me?

00:08:31.160 --> 00:08:32.400
Are we going home or not?

00:08:51.080 --> 00:08:52.120
What happened?

00:08:52.600 --> 00:08:53.440
Mom, I'm fine.

00:08:53.440 --> 00:08:54.680
I just fell by accident.

00:08:54.680 --> 00:08:56.480
Are you hurt anywhere else?

00:08:56.480 --> 00:08:57.440
I'm fine.

00:09:01.300 --> 00:09:02.240
You know it hurts, huh?

00:09:02.240 --> 00:09:03.720
Why weren't you more careful, then?

00:09:05.560 --> 00:09:06.480
Now, it's gone.

00:09:06.480 --> 00:09:07.440
Stop being mischievous.

00:09:08.312 --> 00:09:09.072
By the way, Mom,

00:09:09.072 --> 00:09:10.992
is there any news from the group?

00:09:10.992 --> 00:09:11.992
I've already come up

00:09:12.050 --> 00:09:13.570
with a solution.

00:09:15.840 --> 00:09:16.440
However,

00:09:16.440 --> 00:09:17.280
I just married into

00:09:17.280 --> 00:09:19.080
the Lu family not long ago.

00:09:19.240 --> 00:09:22.440
Some of the older employees there
don't like me.

00:09:22.920 --> 00:09:23.520
At this time,

00:09:23.520 --> 00:09:26.160
if I transfer you to the group by force,

00:09:26.160 --> 00:09:27.880
it'll be difficult for you
to work there.

00:09:29.920 --> 00:09:31.640
Therefore, I've come up with a solution.

00:09:31.640 --> 00:09:33.040
Let's visit the company with some gifts.

00:09:33.040 --> 00:09:34.240
What gifts?

00:09:34.720 --> 00:09:37.240
There's a family called
the Shu family in Hai City.

00:09:37.240 --> 00:09:38.440
They made their fortune
in manufacturing.

00:09:38.440 --> 00:09:39.640
They're very wealthy.

00:09:40.040 --> 00:09:42.320
Mr. Lu wanted to join hands with them
for a few years.

00:09:42.800 --> 00:09:44.440
But Mr. Shu

00:09:44.440 --> 00:09:45.360
was quite conservative.

00:09:45.360 --> 00:09:46.320
He kept rejecting him.

00:09:46.760 --> 00:09:48.240
Therefore, I made an inquiry.

00:09:48.240 --> 00:09:50.280
His youngest daughter
is called Shu Jiajia.

00:09:51.360 --> 00:09:52.640
In my opinion,

00:09:53.280 --> 00:09:55.960
if we establish
a close relationship with Shu Jiajia,

00:09:56.020 --> 00:09:57.800
I think we'll be able
to persuade Mr. Shu.

00:09:58.640 --> 00:09:59.880
I understand now.

00:09:59.880 --> 00:10:00.760
You're treating me

00:10:00.760 --> 00:10:02.240
as the gift here, huh?

00:10:03.040 --> 00:10:03.840
Who said so?

00:10:03.840 --> 00:10:04.920
How can I bear to do that?

00:10:05.700 --> 00:10:06.280
Alright now.

00:10:06.880 --> 00:10:07.760
I need to pack up.

00:10:07.760 --> 00:10:10.440
I'm going to
the basketball friendly this afternoon.

00:10:11.120 --> 00:10:12.360
Basketball friendly?

00:10:13.880 --> 00:10:14.520
Hey.

00:10:14.520 --> 00:10:16.080
You know how to play basketball, right?

00:10:16.100 --> 00:10:17.700
You should show them your skills later.

00:10:23.750 --> 00:10:28.250
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

00:10:28.475 --> 00:10:32.263
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

00:10:32.438 --> 00:10:36.513
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

00:10:36.513 --> 00:10:40.650
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

00:10:40.775 --> 00:10:44.550
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

00:10:44.550 --> 00:10:48.325
♪I'll learn to stop
longing for what's gone♪

00:10:48.325 --> 00:10:50.600
♪The you in my memories♪

00:10:50.600 --> 00:10:52.613
♪Will fade from clarity♪

00:10:52.613 --> 00:10:58.050
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

00:10:59.613 --> 00:11:05.050
♪Forget you completely♪